data.description: Great Investment Opportunity In the Heart of the Popular Montavilla Neighborhood! Solid and charming bungalow ready for your updates. Spacious living room with wood burning fireplace opens to formal dining room with coved ceilings. Bright kitchen leads to laundry and backyard. 2 beds and full bath on main and 3 bedrooms upstairs (one may be non-conforming). Huge 2-car garage, Fenced sunny backyard. Within steps of food carts, Montavilla Park and Montavilla Community Center. Just blocks from popular cafes, the Observatory, theatre, shopping, public transportation. Zoned CE per City of Portland. Buyer to perform their own due diligence about development opportunities. SOLD AS-IS. Seller to do no repairs nor offer credit towards repairs. [Home Energy Score = 1. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222932]
